guest_message: Hi there! I’d like to place an order for my grandkids and me. I need 2 Kids Chicken Tenders meals, 1 Kids Mac and Cheese, and 1 Fish and Chips. Can we get the chicken tenders with BBQ sauce and apple slices, and the mac and cheese with a fruit cup and apple juice?

No, I’m good with the regular Fish and Chips. Just the standard one, please. So we have the 2 Kids Chicken Tenders meals, 1 Kids Mac and Cheese, and 1 Fish and Chips. Can you get me the total, please?
